name: Hopetoun Falls - 3rd Edition
description:
Hopetoun Falls, in The Otways region of Victoria, Australia.

This piece is a single edition of a larger collection of edits, some more outrageous than others. I've always enjoyed experimenting with creative manipulation of colour palettes in my work, but I've always felt pressured to dial it back for publishing on social media. 

This project is an attempt to break free of the restrictions I've placed on myself, and let the community decide what they like best.


Shot on Fujifilm X-T2.


Video is provided in 2160 x 3840 resolution for use in high definition digital displays.
